result.execSummary:
The defendant was charged with both OWI (4th w/in 5 yrs) [Modifiers: General Alcohol Concentration Enhancer, Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (4th Offense)] and Operating w/ PAC (4th w/in 5 yrs) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (4th Offense)]. The defendant was found guilty of OWI (4th w/in 5 yrs) [Modifiers: General Alcohol Concentration Enhancer, Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (4th Offense)] and the other charge, Operating w/ PAC (4th w/in 5 yrs) [Modifiers: Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (4th Offense)] was dismissed by the court.

  • Michael Eduard Gonzalez II was found guilty of OWI (4th w/in 5 yrs) [Modifiers: General Alcohol Concentration Enhancer, Penalty - Operating While under the Influence (4th Offense)], a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(1)(a).
